{"tid":601881,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"同學霸做groupmate 好辛苦","createTime":"2018-03-22T14:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T15:12:02.000Z","uid":17689,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b98ff066817114d880c383af7be2f48bdd62b6c9","tid":601881,"uid":17689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:30:56.000Z","msg":"有咩錯永遠都講到好似因為其他人錯先會錯咁<br />\n係prof面前就永遠推晒啲責任落人地度<br />\n又成日好睇唔起人 覺得咩都可以自己做晒<br />\n自己做錯就係小事唔影響 人地做錯就好大反應要比佢罵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGroupmate 既存在對佢黎講係阻住晒 做佢groupmate 就係幫佢執頭執尾<br />\n冇teamwork 可言<br />\n一組交一份功課就同你講一人做一份再睇下點 結果自己做完就交左上去 其他人做左成個星期既野就完全冇機會交 白費晒<br />\n講野既語氣又好似成日都睇你啲學渣唔起咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底係咪所有學霸都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d028588360cb3ffde67e77f23df9b32d67e496","tid":601881,"uid":14606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"你咪交先過佢 再晤係hea做即交拖死佢"},{"pid":"c961df6afa7a696661c9aed756592a6fa002527f","tid":601881,"uid":87229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:43:11.000Z","msg":"睇唔起人呢點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識多少少野扮大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a16b214c295e1205fa17e0ea54dee400889c3e8c","tid":601881,"uid":90392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:45:47.000Z","msg":"又垬用語, 學霸你老味"},{"pid":"b2bbbb548e75aaa4344c7c58cfb19fa1bb42042a","tid":601881,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"你唔係因為同學霸做野辛苦<br />\n係因為條契弟係一個撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同撚樣做野實辛苦架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e02b5e3d2181e6f9fa966f44166a97b01bebbba1","tid":601881,"uid":138878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"利用完咪算囉，咁讓諗會開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0174eccf9cafb9e058036c20188e4b9a36089cc","tid":601881,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:56:24.000Z","msg":"老實講係我就串到佢仆街啦<br />\n份野你自己做晒然後可以話我錯做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e70724ebfffe866efae90efd31ae436ca2babe63","tid":601881,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:59:06.000Z","msg":"呢啲根本係假學霸<br />\n<br />\n學霸一係自己做 一係叫人唔洗做"},{"pid":"f6bb64fbb41ffc4328a19fdb2223a8875463b5fe","tid":601881,"uid":130268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"咁就你做初一我做十五<br />\n一於全程free ride<br />\n條氣順左,時間多左，成績又好左"},{"pid":"d59c2f1b2b877dc4b1da8515a7d19d0458f07b86","tid":601881,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:01:32.000Z","msg":"霸你老母臭西"},{"pid":"e651e537778d17ce8317409d3414b616f45705e3","tid":601881,"uid":13454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:01:42.000Z","msg":"點睇自己啲groupmate攬住做曬所有野然後話你freeride唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4ee8778150e94979e3eaa54adabfbe86b63aa0","tid":601881,"uid":139606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:02:26.000Z","msg":"老師，佢隻手過界呀！"},{"pid":"cffd4c6a07f3b9f39ab6457be83fef51efb9eb63","tid":601881,"uid":55011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:06:15.000Z","msg":"我以前多數自己寫哂 叫人影相比返過程我 D lab report自己砌就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時候你加隻手埋黎我仲做唔切 不如你都係坐埋一邊啦 我保證做完唔拖低你就得啦<br />\n<br />\n我唔介意人freeride但係介意人唔識扮識仲要亂咁搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地亦都唔洗交lab report比我 因為除左自己我邊個都唔信"},{"pid":"add376d34be2d5c3c75352100d7886835291511f","tid":601881,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T15:12:02.000Z","msg":"吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}